x4freetext: THE DATA GIVEN IN 71KNOX HAVE BEEN EXTRACTED FROM A

SOLVE DISCREPANCIES ABOVE 0.5 KEV WITH OTHER
THE 60 MEV LINEAR ACCELERATOR OF THE CBNM.
